Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.18,0:00:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This is—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.71,0:00:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,A bandage?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.99,0:00:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We’ve given him to the humans\N to bring out vengeful feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.06,0:00:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and hate against them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.37,0:00:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,How cruel...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.01,0:00:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do I have to go through something like this?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.72,0:00:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So now you understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.55,0:00:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re nothing more than an cocky idiot who\N only asks for help when in need.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.36,0:00:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s it... {\alpha&FF&}Do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.72,0:00:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s it... Do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.24,0:00:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Find your true self!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.54,0:00:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,There’s an intruder!\N Hat has entered!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.89,0:00:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Has he come to save Nagai?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.06,0:00:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,After abandoning him...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.69,0:00:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously, why all the fuss?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.15,0:00:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If the great Ogura Ikuya is here—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.15,0:00:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Nagai-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.27,0:00:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.54,0:00:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Satou-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.90,0:00:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m sorry for causing you trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.84,0:00:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This mission...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.14,0:01:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Has been a failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.12,0:01:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let’s go. {\alpha&FF&}We can’t stay longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.50,0:01:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let’s go. We can’t stay longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.49,0:01:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
