Dialogue: 1,0:02:48.52,0:02:53.02,Episode Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(900,0)\blur0.6\pos(549,369)}out of you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.53,0:03:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that draw your attention?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.08,0:03:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Not especially.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.79,0:03:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Protecting this place was these people's work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.89,0:03:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, he’s dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.37,0:03:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s true.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.22,0:03:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,On the other hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.55,0:03:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to get out of here at any cost.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.13,0:03:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So I’ll let you take care of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.76,0:03:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, let’s hurry up then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.76,0:03:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,625)}This kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.10,0:03:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,625)}Made me remember the confusion I felt the first time I saw him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.86,0:03:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,625)}He seemed worried about his sister,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.35,0:03:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,625)}but there was something false about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.98,0:03:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\move(640,625,640,685,1000,1500)}This kid has something strange,\N besides being an Ajin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.08,0:03:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought the mission had failed,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.85,0:03:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,but I think I’ll observe him a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.02,0:04:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.83,0:04:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We’re not security guards!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.91,0:04:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.12,0:04:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.93,0:04:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to kill them?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.41,0:04:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.83,0:04:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We can’t let anyone alive.
Comment: 0,0:04:25.86,0:04:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagai-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.41,0:04:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s just that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.86,0:04:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m sorry to do this after you saved me, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.97,0:04:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,They’re unarmed...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.64,0:04:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it’s not necessary to kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.93,0:04:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,They could be hiding narcotic guns.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.11,0:04:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, we could leave them blind...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.87,0:04:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Or break their arms...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.64,0:04:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagai-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.62,0:04:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.13,0:04:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You are a failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.42,0:05:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You have shot me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.08,0:05:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.32,0:05:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It was an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.41,0:05:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagai...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.93,0:05:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.29,0:05:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.82,0:05:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The IBM is matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.34,0:05:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why can’t we see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.74,0:05:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you see this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.82,0:05:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s time to learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.45,0:05:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The light emitted from its source gets reflected in matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.65,0:05:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The eye senses it and that’s why we see things.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.63,0:05:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, why is glass transparent?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.44,0:05:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s because glass is made of substances that let light go through.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.54,0:05:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Normal glasses have a\N transparency rate of 80% to 90%.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.09,0:05:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The IBM has a transparency rate of 100%.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.38,0:05:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s made of an unknown matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.52,0:05:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t take it so seriously, Riku-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.37,0:06:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,He is the man who does nothing\N but spit out baseless hypothesis.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.71,0:06:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,In Japan, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.84,0:06:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that you have been recognised by a dumb country.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.97,0:06:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that make you so happy, Ikuya-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.27,0:06:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s because of that mindset\N that you can’t step it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.44,0:06:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Kishi-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.40,0:06:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He won’t come out...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.04,0:06:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The repair room is out of our sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.94,0:06:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Tosaki-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.01,0:06:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I won’t need to fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.98,0:06:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.84,0:06:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,If they get here, who will protect me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.94,0:06:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.05,0:06:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t go anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.76,0:06:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.94,0:06:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.59,0:07:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We don’t have any weapons, or a map.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.73,0:07:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I escape?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.98,0:07:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Who would have thought\N I’d have to hide with an Ajin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.56,0:07:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.48,0:07:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He has saved us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.53,0:07:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuck me! In the first place he was the one that brought him here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.87,0:07:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,How many people do you think have died because of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.98,0:07:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven’t killed them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.75,0:07:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,In the first place, if we keep this up...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.38,0:07:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s not like I’ve forgotten what you did to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.50,0:07:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll send you back to the lab!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.04,0:07:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I don’t want to! {\alpha&FF&}I don’t want to go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.11,0:07:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I don’t want to! I don’t want to go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.82,0:07:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll get out of here at any cost.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.86,0:07:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You also want to get out, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.77,0:07:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Our objectives are the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.12,0:07:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We’re even.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.27,0:07:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll be the bait so you can get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.73,0:07:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,In exchange, you’ll show me the escape route,\N so I can get out of here safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.78,0:08:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really going to be the bait?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.80,0:08:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, I can’t die.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.36,0:08:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s not true...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.55,0:08:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.47,0:08:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s settled.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.88,0:08:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagai-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.76,0:08:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.28,0:08:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be confident on your \Ninability to die, I’m guessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.40,0:08:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn’t exaggerating when I said\N I was going to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.31,0:08:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Ajin can die.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.18,0:08:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop talking about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.60,0:08:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Although that depends on how you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.49,0:08:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The resurrection of an Ajin starts\N with the biggest chunk of flesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.04,0:08:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,However, the flesh that has gone \Ntoo far away is not recovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.00,0:08:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead, new flesh is created.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.94,0:08:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If that happens
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.41,0:08:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,with your head...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.79,0:08:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll promise you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.39,0:08:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll cut off your head,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.03,0:08:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and then put it in front of your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.89,0:09:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll make you see how a new head grows, until you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.28,0:09:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The question is, who will be {\i1}you{\i0} then?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.59,0:09:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The new head that will be created,\N or the head that's right here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.41,0:09:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{FIXME}With this, it all ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.39,0:09:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll make you regret to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.27,0:09:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,For killing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.29,0:09:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagai...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.29,0:09:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Kei-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.31,0:09:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You don’t need to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.05,0:09:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.71,0:09:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll make you both get outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.18,0:09:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s what I have to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.73,0:09:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.12,0:10:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,He’ll try to hit me in the back.\N If he hits me there, I’ll be able to revive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.05,0:10:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What’re you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.27,0:10:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn’t we promise it to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.46,0:10:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If you help him escape, I'm not responsible\N for what happens next!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.96,0:10:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I shouldn’t have...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.58,0:10:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Goddamnit... {\alpha&FF&}Why does this has to happen to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.60,0:10:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Goddamnit... Why does this has to happen to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.75,0:10:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.93,0:11:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is there so much of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.05,0:11:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}It’s time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.30,0:11:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}I’ll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.66,0:11:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.56,0:11:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagai-kun’s ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.00,0:11:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,800)}How about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.16,0:11:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s true that the black ghost can cast some words...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.57,0:11:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is just ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.89,0:11:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,800)}Sorry for the inconvenience.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.63,0:12:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,A human made with unknown matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.68,0:12:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And how's that related to the Ajin's immortality?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.08,0:12:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do people eat tangerines?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.80,0:12:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Serves you right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.43,0:12:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That thing saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.32,0:12:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,People can’t make vitamin C by themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.20,0:12:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s why they have to get it from fruits.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.17,0:12:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The black ghost...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.45,0:12:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The Ajin can draw those things out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.01,0:12:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,When those who die from malnutrition revive,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.36,0:12:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,they can even produce those nutrients.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.24,0:12:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But that doesn’t have anything to do with their immortality!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.85,0:12:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s impossible for it to not be related
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.48,0:12:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,to the unknown matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.61,0:13:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.22,0:13:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll survive in this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.49,0:13:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If he follows the lines,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.83,0:13:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(2280,0,1,\c&HBEBEBE&\3c&HBEBEBE&\4c&HBEBEBE&)}he might catch up to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.87,0:13:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.26,0:13:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-{\alpha&FF&}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.51,0:13:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.81,0:13:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.52,0:13:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,When I’m under intense emotions, sometimes humans are able to see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.23,0:13:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s the bloodlust, or something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.77,0:14:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.87,0:14:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m sorry, but I can’t do that, because...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.81,0:14:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1000)}I like to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.84,0:14:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagai-kun! {\alpha&FF&}Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.64,0:14:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagai-kun! Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.51,0:14:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.17,0:14:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I have to show you the way out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.55,0:14:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}That isn’t necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.72,0:14:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.12,0:14:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I hope I can die from this height.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.76,0:14:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}But I wasn’t waiting you only because of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.18,0:15:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}When you get down there,\N I can take you somewhere with my car.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.21,0:15:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.67,0:15:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I’ve always been telling myself that this is my job,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.66,0:15:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}but truth is, I have done really bad things.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.88,0:15:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Besides, there’s something else I’d like you to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.82,0:15:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,625)}You... Are just as how you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.18,0:15:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,625)}During the experiment, your head wasn’t cut, not even once.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.96,0:15:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\move(640,625,640,685,1000,1500)}There were also no traces of brain tissue at the crash site.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.92,0:15:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted you to know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.67,0:15:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you get worried so easily for other people?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.80,0:15:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you understand human pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.24,0:15:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ve never... been worried for someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.74,0:15:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagai-kun... Just as I thought, you’re interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.00,0:15:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Including the personality that your sister talked about.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.83,0:15:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So they both asked you,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.60,0:15:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,how your brother was.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.86,0:15:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.23,0:15:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And what did you tell them?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.16,0:15:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,He is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.58,0:16:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.21,0:16:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The wind is strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.72,0:16:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.81,0:16:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The worst?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.74,0:16:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It can’t b—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.26,0:16:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H00002A&}He’s the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.44,0:16:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,His real personality is rational,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.89,0:16:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and extremely cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.84,0:16:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,He...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.99,0:16:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Is like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.91,0:16:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If he’s dead, I don’t know how to save him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.76,0:16:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Shortest distance is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.06,0:16:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.12,0:16:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,How unlucky, I ran out of bullets.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.63,0:16:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.61,0:17:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the last level, Nagai-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.96,0:17:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Goddamnit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.52,0:17:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey ghost! Come out again!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.38,0:17:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Come out again!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.52,0:17:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It came!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.40,0:17:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m under the rain but... Well, it doesn’t matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.21,0:17:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he aiming for the head?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.14,0:17:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You aim to the head too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.24,0:17:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}Why did you always make jokes like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.96,0:17:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, very good. So it can ignore your orders too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.70,0:18:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,950)}I only played with him because it made me sad to see him alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.23,0:18:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t say things from so long ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.38,0:18:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagai-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.67,0:18:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Run...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.12,0:18:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.60,0:18:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.52,0:18:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn’t want to get related with anyone,\N nor I had that need.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.71,0:18:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Neither I cared about others.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.21,0:18:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.86,0:18:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.98,0:18:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s why...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.58,0:18:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m going to let you fall from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.42,0:18:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s the only choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.92,0:18:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If he manages to fall in the grass,\N the chances of survival are greater.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.53,0:18:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s him! {\alpha&FF&}It’s Nagai Kei!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.40,0:18:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s him! It’s Nagai Kei!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.60,0:18:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like he wants to drop a member\N from the research team.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.68,0:18:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he taking him as hostage?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.19,0:18:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you thinking? At this rate he’ll run away!
Comment: 0,0:18:59.99,0:18:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Tosaki-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.21,0:19:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouma Riku-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.08,0:19:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.23,0:19:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,How much...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.89,0:19:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,How much time would it take\N the Anti-Ajin special force to be ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.76,0:19:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t joke with that! {FIXME}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.28,0:19:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s nothing more than a special force that appeared\N when the existence of the Ajin was discovered!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.04,0:19:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Kouma Riku-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.93,0:19:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We have yet to find a solution to this situation.\N It’s impossible to make the troops go—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.13,0:19:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H281000&}This is our chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.85,0:19:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.55,0:19:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H281000&}Why didn’t hat use his IBM today?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.71,0:19:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t you think it’s strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.06,0:19:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,He wasn’t able to use it today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.69,0:19:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I don’t know the reason, but that possibility is high.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.07,0:19:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,There’s a big difference between this assault and the one from Tanaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.40,0:19:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,There won’t be another chance like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.13,0:19:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Riku-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.25,0:19:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Bend your legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.13,0:19:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.15,0:19:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.36,0:19:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.20,0:19:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.80,0:20:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you going to fight now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.16,0:20:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,800)}Aim to the head too...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.81,0:20:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,These were the memories from...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.41,0:20:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I could see some of Nagai-kun's memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.30,0:20:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So that’s what happens when the heads collide.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.46,0:20:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagai-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.30,0:20:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.19,0:20:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he let him go?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.38,0:20:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood. {\alpha&FF&}It’s ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.34,0:20:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood. It’s ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.72,0:20:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Nevertheless, if this theory is correct...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.15,0:20:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor Ogura, you were listening, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.82,0:21:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,IBM is not as efficient as you guys think.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.93,0:21:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,There are lots of conditions to use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.53,0:21:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you see it, Nagai-Kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.80,0:21:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That river is a channel that leads\N to the sea on rainy days.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.50,0:21:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If you get in it, maybe you’ll make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.50,0:21:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor, please refrain from giving out\N information about the Ajin.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.98,0:21:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, it’s true.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.88,0:21:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So... No comments.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.32,0:21:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.64,0:21:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagai Kei has jumped to the river!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.75,0:22:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.69,0:22:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m leaving. The sample has run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.79,0:22:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Nagai Kei has jumped from the rooftop to the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.08,0:22:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}After he let go to someone that looked like an investigator, he jumped to the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.58,0:22:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}The water of the river, because of the rain...
Comment: 0,0:22:21.61,0:22:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan...
